per和Swarm。"}, :properties {:color "yellow"}} {:id #uuid "61e14ed4-5a34-4163-9a52-f44580ad1f8e", :page 53, :position {:bounding {:x1 93.15324401855469, :y1 181.93231201171875, :x2 640.9239501953125, :y2 254.35577392578125, :width 741, :height 958.9411764705882}, :rects ({:x1 506.23919677734375, :y1 181.93231201171875, :x2 640.9239501953125, :y2 207.0362548828125, :width 741, :height 958.9411764705882} {:x1 542.1597290039062, :y1 185.05841064453125, :x2 640.9239501953125, :y2 202.55511474609375, :width 741, :height 958.9411764705882} {:x1 93.15324401855469, :y1 207.91586303710938, :x2 611.9232788085938, :y2 233.01983642578125, :width 741, :height 958.9411764705882} {:x1 93.15324401855469, :y1 210.19802856445312, :x2 611.9232788085938, :y2 227.69473266601562, :width 741, :height 958.9411764705882} {:x1 93.15324401855469, :y1 233.05545043945312, :x2 129.0624542236328, :y2 254.35577392578125, :width 741, :height 958.9411764705882}), :page 53}, :content {:text "2015年7月30日，第一个以太坊区块被挖矿成功。“世界计算机”开始为全世界提供服务。"}, :properties {:color "green"}} {:id #uuid "61e152b4-92c3-4b7f-a9dd-5def50e0196c", :page 55, :position {:bounding {:x1 122.6875, :y1 634.625, :x2 832.3733520507812, :y2 795.09375, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117}, :rects ({:x1 453.867919921875, :y1 634.625, :x2 832.3732299804688, :y2 662.625, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117} {:x1 122.6875, :y1 667.734375, :x2 832.3732299804688, :y2 695.734375, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117} {:x1 122.6875, :y1 670.734375, :x2 832.3732299804688, :y2 693.734375, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117} {:x1 122.6875, :y1 700.859375, :x2 832.3733520507812, :y2 728.859375, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117} {:x1 122.6875, :y1 703.859375, :x2 832.3733520507812, :y2 726.859375, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117} {:x1 122.6875, :y1 733.96875, :x2 808.7264404296875, :y2 761.96875, :width 975.9999999999999, :height 1263.0588235294117